    // TODO: Yikes, in need of refactor
    #about
      .container
        .section-header-container
          h2 HEY THERE
          p IT'S NICE TO MEET YOU
        .about-video.col-sm-5
        .section-text-container.col-sm-5.pull-right
          h3 MY PASSION IS CREATING EXPERIENCES
          p I believe that like music, good design is found between the notes. Design should convey just enough to tell the story of a brand while still leaving the rest up to the user’s imagination. When I discovered development I was hooked, now I use code as another medium to craft engaging experiences.<br><br>I believe that engagement stems from a user's ability to empathize with a product. It’s never just a product that’s being developed, it’s the feeling that it envokes as well. It's with this perspective that I approach both my personal and professional projects.


      .about-interests.section-container
        .container
          .section-text-container.col-sm-5
            h3 CURRENTLY LISTENING TO:
            p A widget calling the last.fm API will be here
          .section-text-container.col-sm-5.pull-right
            h3 INTERESTS:
            ul
              li • Endlessly scrolling through Dribbble
              li • Interjecting with songs from Frozen
              li • Consuming copious amounts of coffee
              li • Corgis

